Quarterback Kevin Kolb Is Going to Cardinals From Eagles, ESPN Reports

-- B y   L a r r y   S i d d o n s
-- 
2011-07-28T20:11:31Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-28/quarterback-kevin-kolb-is-going-to-cardinals-from-eagles-espn-reports.html
Quarterback Kevin Kolb is being
traded to the  Arizona Cardinals  from the  Philadelphia Eagles ,
ESPN.com said.  The Eagles will get cornerback Dominique Rodgers-Cromartie
and a second-round draft pick, ESPN said, citing unidentified
people.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Larry Siddons at 
 lsiddons@bloomberg.net  